body:
Ok, so when you have enough mastery tokens (whether for lvl 6 or lvl 7 mastery) there are 3 options.
First option is &quot; Unlock with 2 tokens and 500 blue essense&quot;
Second option is &quot;Unlock with 2 tokens and 1 Champion permanent&quot;
And the third and final option is &quot; 2 toekns and 1 graves shard&quot;


So if someone has the champion already unlocked whether through ip or RP, the 2nd option should allow us to unlock the mastery for that champion regardless of blue essense or shards. Why is that we cant unlock the mastery even when i already own the champion ( 2nd option).

Is it a bug or something??..really wanna know{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
